13:07.170 --> 13:09.035
This juror thinks
Lloyd Garber is lying,

13:09.090 --> 13:11.172
that he could never
remember a damning
conversation with Peter.

13:11.220 --> 13:15.008
So you want me to try to talk to
this juror's doubts without...

13:15.050 --> 13:16.961
seeming to?Yes.

13:17.010 --> 13:20.093
Any thoughts on how to do that?

13:20.140 --> 13:21.698
