24:22.060 --> 24:23.402
by roughly the same amount

24:23.460 --> 24:24.711
as Harry's.They can all show

24:24.760 --> 24:26.489
verified losses
from gun crimes?

24:26.550 --> 24:28.848
And I can probably
find you a few more

24:28.900 --> 24:31.152
if I have a little time.No, this is amazing.

24:31.200 --> 24:33.156
CARY:
Perfect. We can use this
as a class action.

24:33.210 --> 24:34.939
DIANE:
No, first we use it

24:34.990 --> 24:37.038
mmsmm.
Even as a test balloon.

24:37.080 --> 24:39.901
[indistinct conversations]

24:44.830 --> 24:45.956
Jason.

24:46.000 --> 24:47.956
What?

24:48.000 --> 24:50.525
I can't just take an office.

24:50.570 --> 24:51.741
JASON:
I agree.

24:51.790 --> 24:53.178
LUCCA:
Well, come on, then.

24:53.230 --> 24:54.652
Help me move it back.

24:54.710 --> 24:56.780
I didn't move you
there. Diane did.

24:56.840 --> 24:59.001
Diane.

24:59.060 --> 25:00.186
What?

25:00.230 --> 25:01.629
Why?

25:01.670 --> 25:03.103
I don't know.

25:05.670 --> 25:07.672
But congratulations.

25:12.200 --> 25:14.191
Thank you.

25:20.600 --> 25:23.160
I need a minute of your time.

25:23.210 --> 25:25.201
Sounds serious.

25:27.700 --> 25:31.124
Who were you seeing last night
at the Avenue Tavern?

25:31.180 --> 25:33.478
Who was I seeing?Yes.

25:35.960 --> 25:37.746
You know, this seems
like a subject

25:37.790 --> 25:40.008
that we don't usually
delve into.

25:40.060 --> 25:41.573
Yes, but this is not usual.

25:41.620 --> 25:43.884
How do you know
I was with anyone?

25:43.930 --> 25:45.090
Alicia saw you.

25:51.110 --> 25:52.668
What did she see?

25:52.720 --> 25:55.154
You... kissing this woman.

25:59.860 --> 26:01.987
It was a friend from New York.

26:02.030 --> 26:03.509
How serious a friend?

26:03.560 --> 26:04.902
Was Alicia upset?

26:04.950 --> 26:06.679
Why would she
be upset?

26:06.730 --> 26:08.812
You're not married, right?
