26:08.870 --> 26:10.906
Does she know
that you're talking to me?

26:10.960 --> 26:12.689
No.

26:12.740 --> 26:14.731
What are you gonna do?

26:18.700 --> 26:20.691
I don't know.

26:22.920 --> 26:24.262
[indistinct conversations]

26:24.320 --> 26:26.788
Okay. Yeah.
Oh, uh...

26:26.840 --> 26:28.091
Mrs. Florrick.
Hello.

26:28.150 --> 26:29.924
Thank you so much
for being here today.

26:29.970 --> 26:33.269
It's not by choice, Mr. Fox.
I was subpoenaed.

26:33.330 --> 26:35.275
Well, thank you anyway.

26:35.330 --> 26:37.286
I don't want to make this
any more confrontational

26:37.330 --> 26:38.638
than it has to be.

26:38.680 --> 26:41.934
So, please, just have
a seat right here.

26:41.990 --> 26:44.550
I have several questions
I think the grand jury

26:44.600 --> 26:46.420
would like to hear
the answers to, um,

26:46.470 --> 26:48.290
but I understand
that you have a right

26:48.340 --> 26:50.126
