26:50.170 --> 26:51.865
I do.Good.

26:51.910 --> 26:53.684
I just don't want
the jury to judge you

26:53.740 --> 26:55.640
every time you say "I
invoke spousal privilege

26:55.700 --> 26:57.509
and elect not to
answer the question."

26:57.570 --> 26:58.958
Thank you.

26:59.000 --> 27:00.695
So, members of the grand jury,

27:00.740 --> 27:03.049
please refrain
from any such judgment.

27:03.090 --> 27:04.352
Now I'd like
to turn

27:04.400 --> 27:05.788
to our first question.
[clears throat]

27:05.840 --> 27:07.922
Mrs. Florrick, did your husband

27:07.970 --> 27:09.619
ever make a deal
with Lloyd Garber

27:09.670 --> 27:11.058
to have his
son released

27:11.100 --> 27:13.148
in trade for political
contributions?

27:13.190 --> 27:14.407
No.

27:15.720 --> 27:17.199
Uh... Mrs. Florrick,

27:17.240 --> 27:19.196
just to be clear,
you answered that question.

27:19.240 --> 27:20.753
Yes, I did.

27:20.810 --> 27:23.244
Well, if you
answer this question,

27:23.290 --> 27:26.191
